al, 2001), MC (Miller and Charles, 1991) and RG (Rubenstein and Goodenough, 1965), have beenwidely used to evaluate vector-space models.
			Moti vated to evaluate composition models, Mitchell andLapata (2008) introduced a dataset where an intransitive verb, presented with a subject noun, is com pared to another verb chosen to be either similar or dissimilar to the intransitive verb in context.
			The context is short, with only one word, and only verbs are compared.
