			(2008), Thater et al (2011) and Dinu and Lapata (2010) evaluated wordsimilarity in context with a modified task where systems are to rerank gold-standard paraphrase candi dates given the SemEval 2007 Lexical SubstitutionTask dataset.
			This task only indirectly evaluates sim ilarity as only reranking of already similar words are evaluated.
	
	
